content:
I just finished up a Welcome Zoom meeting - the link that was shared to join a phone bank is not working - I keep getting a message stating that I have to log in via my commercial Zoom account.
This is the link that I was given:

Stephen Bronskill (Harris for President): ðŸ“žJoin todayâ€™s 9pm ET Phone Bank shift: https://democrats.zoom.us/j/95357918984?pwd=gGpGUPc6ZpbB8A7XyhrsQMSswpF2eq.1

Would someone please tell me where I can find a link that will let me join? Thank you!
That was the correct link. You do have to create a Zoom Workplace account and log into it to get into the Zoom Phone Bank. The Zoom Workplace account is free.
Thanks for the info! I will be ready for next time!
